1. *To* je zakon. (That is the law.)
2. On ima dovoljno novca da *to* kupi. (He has enough money to buy that.)
3. Učenje je lakše ako *to* volite. (Learning is easier if you love it.)
4. Moraš da poštuješ *to*. (You must respect that.)
5. Ona je dovoljno stara da *to* shvati. (She is old enough to understand that.)
6. *To* je sve što treba da znaš. (That is all you need to know.)